{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cd4a570d7d","title":"大字报——急流勇退！","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ca8d78ca87","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"cd4a570d7d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"5cd6c93a1b","name":"张丽中"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d1121b1656","type":"title","text":"大字报——急流勇退！","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"},{"id":"e6032e486d","type":"authors","text":"北京大学张景中","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"},{"id":"8e78f6a693","type":"subtitle","text":"（张景中：北京大学数学系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"},{"id":"bd68525b3c","type":"paragraph","text":"急流勇退！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"},{"id":"3747a5783d","type":"paragraph","text":"1．我大体上同意杨路“最后的宣言”中所讲的话。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"},{"id":"24bfd2c239","type":"paragraph","text":"2．一个月更好地使我知道了政治是怎么会事。它比我能想到的要肮脏得多。我必须保卫自己的灵魂不受沾污。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"},{"id":"1065b2d0fc","type":"paragraph","text":"3．我希望百花学社办下去，为了避免社内分岐。我退出。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"},{"id":"e88a760d5b","type":"paragraph","text":"4．我不参加这次学习了。我要利用这几天休息和玩。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"},{"id":"f5f48af310","type":"paragraph","text":"5．我为了在某种程度上履行自己的诺言、打算：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"},{"id":"78bca5a34b","type":"paragraph","text":"举行一次三害根源的报告会。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"},{"id":"40d507920e","type":"paragraph","text":"和一些已约好的同学稍稍交换一下意见。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"},{"id":"2806ac8331","type":"paragraph","text":"假期里到天津一次，仅仅是为了不失约。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"},{"id":"ddeed8188b","type":"paragraph","text":"6．我永远记住这一月来的情况，并将对我一生中所能遇到的朋友叙述真相。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d"}],"page":{"id":"09d789a870","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cd4a570d7d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}